      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Other [BICEP-XX] tags appear next to the runtime resources they configure.\nUser-side query RBAC (e.g. Monitoring Reader) is NOT in Bicep \u2014 it's the deployer's existing tenant access.",
